  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You are the Undead</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect human essence to summon more undead. Slay the greedy humans and challenge their leaders in Turn-based tactical fights. You are the final boss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/775d8f8307a829304ba34d7b5fa19a1c.poster.avif?t=1761392362\" width=620 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/775d8f8307a829304ba34d7b5fa19a1c.webm?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/775d8f8307a829304ba34d7b5fa19a1c.mp4?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Nemire</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nemire is a daunting union of humanity's mightiest defenders. A symphony of unparalleled skill and cooperation. And they are everything that is wrong with the living. You must raise Undead and destroy greed and power-driven Humans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/544fa5527424a2d4a93639cada2dd0e0.avif?t=1761392362\" width=620 height=153 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based tactical combat</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your squad of ever-evolving undead </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/fdf8ae198b73961046261ef6d9615c2a.poster.avif?t=1761392362\" width=620 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/fdf8ae198b73961046261ef6d9615c2a.webm?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/fdf8ae198b73961046261ef6d9615c2a.mp4?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random unit traits modify how abilities and standard attacks work </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meaningful unit progression</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/34d19e6c049f2d5d6f4ed276e9983f8a.poster.avif?t=1761392362\" width=620 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/34d19e6c049f2d5d6f4ed276e9983f8a.webm?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/34d19e6c049f2d5d6f4ed276e9983f8a.mp4?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meaningful unit progression </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combination of handcrafted and procedural environments </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/f7f49e5466a19b792d97326ac22249bb.poster.avif?t=1761392362\" width=620 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/f7f49e5466a19b792d97326ac22249bb.webm?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/f7f49e5466a19b792d97326ac22249bb.mp4?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gradually ramping difficulty </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Impactful abilities </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/603dea77917eef9abcb4a4330f749ccb.poster.avif?t=1761392362\" width=620 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/603dea77917eef9abcb4a4330f749ccb.webm?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/603dea77917eef9abcb4a4330f749ccb.mp4?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You are the Undead</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect human essence to summon more undead. Slay the greedy humans and challenge their leaders in Turn-based tactical fights. You are the final boss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/775d8f8307a829304ba34d7b5fa19a1c.poster.avif?t=1761392362\" width=620 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/775d8f8307a829304ba34d7b5fa19a1c.webm?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/775d8f8307a829304ba34d7b5fa19a1c.mp4?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Nemire</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nemire is a daunting union of humanity's mightiest defenders. A symphony of unparalleled skill and cooperation. And they are everything that is wrong with the living. You must raise Undead and destroy greed and power-driven Humans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/544fa5527424a2d4a93639cada2dd0e0.avif?t=1761392362\" width=620 height=153 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based tactical combat</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your squad of ever-evolving undead </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/fdf8ae198b73961046261ef6d9615c2a.poster.avif?t=1761392362\" width=620 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/fdf8ae198b73961046261ef6d9615c2a.webm?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/fdf8ae198b73961046261ef6d9615c2a.mp4?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random unit traits modify how abilities and standard attacks work </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meaningful unit progression</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/34d19e6c049f2d5d6f4ed276e9983f8a.poster.avif?t=1761392362\" width=620 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/34d19e6c049f2d5d6f4ed276e9983f8a.webm?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/34d19e6c049f2d5d6f4ed276e9983f8a.mp4?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meaningful unit progression </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combination of handcrafted and procedural environments </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/f7f49e5466a19b792d97326ac22249bb.poster.avif?t=1761392362\" width=620 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1955120/extras/f7f49e5466a19b792d97326ac22249bb.webm?t=1761392362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai